  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7236586/" class="title-link">关于本书的错误</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7236586"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/Binje.S/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1969662-750.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/Binje.S/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">-恰恰恰恰恰</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2014-12-10"
      class="main-meta">2014-12-10 16:43:42</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7236586_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  因为最近的时间不是很充裕，所以纠错慢慢来。今天偶然翻起来的时候一眼就看到要命错误，忍不住爬出来了。 所以以后会陆续把看到的错误更新。  p124第二段第七行： “龙门石窟中年代最早的昙曜五窟。” 应为 “云冈石窟中年代最早的昙曜五窟。”

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/7236586/#comments">(2回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">4有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
